tm:topic_3 dct:description "This topic centers on government policy, legislation, and parliamentary debate concerning agriculture and forestry. It includes discussions by the Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry on agrarian contracts, land use, rural zones and municipalities, crop production (especially viticulture), disaster relief, taxation, market regulation, and support measures for farmers. Overall, it reflects institutional management of the agricultural and forest sectors and their economic, legal, and social dimensions."@en;
