tm:topic_4 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "International military issues"@en;
dct:description "This topic captures parliamentary debate and government positions on war, peace, and international security, with a strong focus on military affairs. It includes discussions on NATO, foreign military bases, intelligence services, defense budgets, Cold War and post?Cold War geopolitics (United States, Soviet Union/Russia), and international missions such as Iraq and peacekeeping operations. Overall, it reflects how Italy's defense and foreign policy are framed in relation to international alliances, conflicts, and national sovereignty."@en;
skos:altLabel "Military and Foreign Policy"@en,"Defense and Security Policy"@en,"International Military Affairs"@en,"War and Peace Politics"@en .
