rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Sicilian related issues"@en;
dct:description "This topic centers on political, institutional, and administrative issues related to Sicily as an autonomous region. It includes debates on the Sicilian Statute, the Regional Assembly, relations between the central government and the region, regional elections, funding and economic interventions, and region-specific emergencies (such as natural disasters). The documents mainly consist of parliamentary discussions addressing Sicily?s autonomy, governance, and political representation."@en;
skos:altLabel "Sicilian Regional Politics"@en,"Sicilian Autonomy"@en,"Regional Governance in Sicily"@en,"Sicily Regional Affairs"@en .
