tm:topic_12 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "European Union"@en;
dct:description "This topic captures parliamentary debate on European integration and the political governance of the European Union. It includes discussions on EU treaties (notably Maastricht and later reforms), ratification processes, the role of national parliaments and the European Parliament, EU foreign and economic policy, enlargement, and the balance of decision-making between EU institutions and member states. Overall, it reflects domestic political deliberation on Europe?s institutional and political development."@en;
skos:altLabel "European Integration Politics"@en,"EU Treaty Politics"@en,"European Union Governance"@en,"EU Institutional Affairs"@en .
