tm:topic_20 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Nuclear energy"@en;
dct:description "This topic covers debates and decisions surrounding nuclear energy, including nuclear power plants, reactors, radioactive waste, safety measures, and international treaties. The documents link civilian and military nuclear issues, focusing on risk management (especially after Chernobyl), public safety, environmental concerns, nuclear disarmament, and international cooperation and regulation in the nuclear sector."@en;
skos:altLabel "Nuclear Energy Policy"@en,"Nuclear Safety and Regulation"@en,"Atomic Energy Governance"@en,"Nuclear Power and Risk"@en .
