tm:topic_28 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Nuclear weapons"@en;
dct:description "This topic centers on political and parliamentary debate in Italy over the installation of nuclear missiles during the Cold War, particularly within the NATO framework. It captures opposition and support surrounding U.S. and NATO missile bases on Italian territory, concerns about nuclear escalation, Soviet?American tensions, national sovereignty, and peace movements advocating disarmament and negotiations (e.g., Geneva talks)."@en;
skos:altLabel "Nuclear Missile Deployment"@en,"NATO Nuclear Missiles"@en,"Cold War Armaments"@en,"Missile Bases and Peace"@en .
