tm:topic_31 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Relations with Somalia"@en;
dct:description "This topic focuses on Italy?s involvement in Somalia through international and military missions, including peacekeeping, humanitarian aid, and reconstruction efforts. The documents discuss parliamentary debates on Italy?s role, coordination with the UN and other countries, political and military challenges, and the provision of international assistance in the context of Somali conflicts."@en;
skos:altLabel "Somalia Humanitarian Missions"@en,"Somalia International Intervention"@en,"Humanitarian and Military Aid"@en,"Italian Foreign Operations"@en .
