tm:topic_33 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Drug addiction"@en;
dct:description "This topic centers on Italy?s political and legislative discussions regarding drug addiction, including prevention, treatment, rehabilitation, and harm reduction strategies. It covers issues such as the use of methadone and other therapeutic interventions, the role of public and private treatment services (e.g., SER.T and therapeutic communities), and the broader societal and legal frameworks for supporting individuals with substance dependence."@en;
skos:altLabel "Drug Addiction Policy"@en,"Substance Abuse Treatment"@en,"Addiction and Rehabilitation"@en,"Drug Harm Reduction"@en .
