tm:topic_35 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Israeli-Palestinian conflict"@en;
dct:description "This topic focuses on the political, diplomatic, and international discussions surrounding the conflict between Israel and Palestine. It covers issues such as peace negotiations, territorial disputes, the role of international organizations (like the UN and EU), recognition of Palestinian statehood, and the broader geopolitical dynamics of the Middle East. The content reflects parliamentary debates and concerns about civilian impacts, security, and the pursuit of a sustainable resolution."@en;
skos:altLabel "Israel-Palestine Conflict"@en,"Middle East Peace"@en,"Palestinian-Israeli Relations"@en,"Arab-Israeli Diplomacy"@en .
