tm:topic_40 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Cuban issue"@en;
dct:description "This topic focuses on the political and human rights situation in Cuba, particularly under Fidel Castro's regime. It highlights issues such as political repression, limitations on freedom and democratic rights, international condemnation, and debates on U.S.-Cuba relations. The discussions emphasize the defense of civil liberties, the rule of law, and international scrutiny of Cuba?s governance."@en;
skos:altLabel "Cuba Human Rights"@en,"Cuban Political Repression"@en,"Cuba and Liberty"@en,"International Human Rights Cuba"@en .
