tm:topic_45 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Electromagnetism and health"@en;
dct:description "This topic focuses on the potential health effects of exposure to electromagnetic fields (EMF), including those from power lines, mobile phones, and other sources. It encompasses scientific uncertainty, public concern, legislative responses, and regulatory measures aimed at reducing EMF exposure and protecting human health. The discussions reflect both the precautionary principle and debates over policy implementation."@en;
skos:altLabel "Electromagnetic Health Risks"@en,"EMF Exposure Regulation"@en,"Electromagnetic Pollution"@en,"Health and EM Fields"@en .
