tm:topic_46 a tm:Topic;
rdfs:comment "A topic is a FrAC observation that groups observable lexical forms (OntoLex Forms) and is observed in a corpus."@en;
skos:prefLabel "Air traffic safety"@en;
dct:description "This topic revolves around the monitoring and control of air traffic with a focus on military operations, radar systems, and aviation safety. It includes discussions on air defense, military exercises, airport security, incidents like the Ustica tragedy, and the coordination between civil and military aviation authorities. The emphasis is on ensuring secure flight operations and addressing gaps or failures in radar coverage and airspace management."@en;
skos:altLabel "Military Air Surveillance"@en,"Air Defense and Radar"@en,"Military Aviation Safety"@en,"Air Traffic Security"@en .
